text: Priscilla Natalia Tapia Castillo (born 2 May 1991) is a Costa Rican footballer who plays as a goalkeeper for Club Sport Herediano the Costa Rica women's national team. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football goalkeepers Category:Costa Rican women's footballers Category:Costa Rica women's international footballers Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Costa Rica Category:Pan American Games medalists in football Category:Footballers at the 2019 Pan American Games
